Package: corpling
Type: Package
Title: Simple Tools for Corpus Linguistics
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Date: 2016-01-01
Authors@R: person("Earl", "Brown", email = "ekbrown77@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Provides simple tools for corpus linguistics, such as the ability to
    produce a concordance of a regular expression and the ability to create frequency
    lists of ngrams.
